  description: "socket.AF_INET.__class__.__qualname__.__eq__('AddressFamily') == True — AF_INET is an AddressFamily IntEnum member; __class__.__qualname__ equals 'AddressFamily'; no prior socket spec checks AF_INET.__class__.__qualname__; first __class__.__qualname__ standalone for socket.AF_INET"
  category: class_attrs
  kind: python_call_eq
